### Create [POST /v1/notifications]

Creates new notification connection and notifies all open and listening streams.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (CreateNotificationPayload)
+ Response 200 (application/json)
  + Attributes (array[ActivityConnectionResponse])

### Update last seen [POST /v1/notifications/last-seen/{activityId}]

Any activity prior to and including requested won't show up in newly open streams.

+ Parameters
  + adminId: 1 (required, number) - Store admin id
  + activityId: 1 (required, number) - Last seen activity id
+ Response 200
  + Attributes (LastSeenActivityResponse)
